title: Enemy.Front.PROPER-CODEX
description:
CODEX PRESENTS:


                         Enemy Front PROPER (c) CI Games

    Release Date :  6/2014                         Protection : Steam
    Discs        :  1                              Genre      : Action


    ENEMY FRONT is the first truly modern WW2 FPS, featuring stunning
    visuals, open-ended levels and a richly interactive combat experience
    that breaks out of the standard model of highly linear scripted FPS
    experiences, giving the player full freedom to own their playing
	style.


   - Extract
   - Burn or mount the .iso
   - Run setup.exe and install
   - Copy crack from CODEX folder to your installdir
   - Play

   PROPER Notes: The RELOADED release crashes on game start.


   Block game exe in your firewall to prevent the game from trying to go
   online ..
